{"tid":1272660,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"（20：00）大批口罩疑似古惑仔經過修頓","createTime":"2019-07-01T12:16:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T12:47:06.000Z","uid":195252,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"31c6f478a0f3b622e5d73c8acb597ab401c9475a","tid":1272660,"uid":195252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T12:16:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bBpPodD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbBpPodD.jpg&h=359cc42e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有圖，小弟親眼目睹，疑似古惑童黨，有領頭人。之後分兩批，一批加入遊行隊伍，另一批前往金鐘立會方向<br />\n大家小心<br />\n<br />\n非搞事post"},{"pid":"5659148c438fc2b6e4e6a4ffa73c9f0dd264707e","tid":1272660,"uid":4050,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T12:17:16.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">共匪一貫手法，分化、滲透，然後拉籠一派打一派，屌嗰啲當然90%都係五毛，但亦都唔排除有真心膠中計信咗佢地一套，呢個就係拉籠一派打一派，群眾鬥群眾，要你自相殘殺，孤立主要敵人，民初時期國民政府分裂就係共匪搞出嚟，共匪玩咗咁多年分化，普羅大眾應該要熟悉呢一點，大家都係擁抱自由民主嘅價值，呢個要保持清醒，同伴之間要互相尊重，唔好咁易上五毛當</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"b2c769018740345f722a8fc8479d16fe60f15025","tid":1272660,"uid":195252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T12:18:01.000Z","msg":"前面白色頭髮係領頭人"},{"pid":"9b4088b972d15e9de2830bfd39801a6f34ac9b6f","tid":1272660,"uid":144187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T12:19:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"43ad64969af6d8f8fcc71fcfb48da6c54444d278","tid":1272660,"uid":195252,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T12:24:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"333ac96327f8382b185eb2c38b8e143d16e9d454","tid":1272660,"uid":167692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T12:25:27.000Z","msg":"咁又點呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3321a77b19e35f264baefb79f678e079062cad51","tid":1272660,"uid":253409,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T12:25:45.000Z","msg":"小心古惑仔搞事<br />\n今